  <h2>The Gradual Path</h2>

  <p>
    The most successful transitions happen slowly. Begin by adding just 25% natural
    litter to your cat's existing litter. Mix thoroughly so the textures blend.
    Observe how your cat responds over 3-5 days.
  </p>

  <p>
    If all seems wellâ€”if your cat continues using the box normally, without hesitation
